		<label>Castellan plate helmet</label>
		<description>An auramite Power Armor helmet supposed to be worn with the Castellan Plate. While it is typically not worn, as the Captain-General usually shows his face to inspire other Custodians, it can still provide excellent protection against all threats.\n\nAfter serving in the Allarus Terminators, a young Trajann Valoris was made a Companion - the three hundred elite Custodians assigned as the Emperors personal guard. However, due to his desire to take the initiative against the Great Enemy, he lasted only twenty-two years before becoming a Shield-Captain - and, a few centuries later, rising to the rank of Captain-General.</description>
